trans-unit.source: Provides a set of services that convert a managed assembly to a COM type library and vice versa.
trans-unit.target: 提供一組服務，將 Managed 組件 (Assembly) 轉換為 COM 型別程式庫，反之亦然。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibConverter" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibConverter" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The assembly to convert.
trans-unit.target: 要進行轉換的組件。

trans-unit.source: The file name of the resulting type library.
trans-unit.target: 產生的型別程式庫的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibExporterFlags" /> value indicating any special settings.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibExporterFlags" /> 值，表示任何特別設定。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibExporterNotifySink" /> interface implemented by the caller.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫端所實作的 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibExporterNotifySink" /> 介面。

trans-unit.source: Converts an assembly to a COM type library.
trans-unit.target: 將組件轉換為 COM 型別程式庫。

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <see langword="ITypeLib" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 實作 <see langword="ITypeLib" /> 介面的物件。

trans-unit.source: For more information on `ITypeLib`, please see its existing documentation in the MSDN library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`ITypeLib`，請參閱 MSDN library 中的現有文件。

trans-unit.source: for permission to call unmanaged code.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫 unmanaged 程式碼的權限。

trans-unit.source: Security Action: Demand.
trans-unit.target: 安全性動作： 需求。

trans-unit.source: Associated Enumeration: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode" />
trans-unit.target: 相關聯的列舉型別： <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode" />

trans-unit.source: Converts a COM type library to an assembly.
trans-unit.target: 將 COM 型別程式庫轉換為組件。

trans-unit.source: The object that implements the <see langword="ITypeLib" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 實作 <see langword="ITypeLib" /> 介面的物件。

trans-unit.source: The file name of the resulting assembly.
trans-unit.target: 產生的組件的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags" /> value indicating any special settings.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags" /> 值，表示任何特別設定。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibImporterNotifySink" /> interface implemented by the caller.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫端所實作的.<see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibImporterNotifySink" /> 介面。

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="byte" /> array containing the public key.
trans-unit.target: 含有公開金鑰的 <see langword="byte" /> 陣列。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Reflection.StrongNameKeyPair" /> object containing the public and private cryptographic key pair.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Reflection.StrongNameKeyPair" /> 物件，含有共用和私密的密碼編譯金鑰組。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="true" />, the interfaces require link time checks for <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode" /> permission.
trans-unit.target: 如果為 <see langword="true" />，則介面需要 <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.UnmanagedCode" /> 使用權限的連結時期檢查。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="false" />, the interfaces require run time checks that require a stack walk and are more expensive, but help provide greater protection.
trans-unit.target: 如果為 <see langword="false" />，則介面就必須進行需要堆疊查核行程 (Stack Walk) 以及較昂貴卻可以協助提供較多保護的執行階段檢查。

trans-unit.source: Converts a COM type library to an assembly.
trans-unit.target: 將 COM 型別程式庫轉換為組件。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder" /> object containing the converted type library.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder" /> 物件，包含已轉換的型別程式庫。

trans-unit.source: If you do not want to generate a strong name for your assembly, it is valid for `publicKey` and `keyPair` to be `null`, as long as `flags` does not equal <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags.PrimaryInteropAssembly?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 如果您不想要產生強式名稱的組件，可供`publicKey`和`keyPair`是`null`，只要`flags`不等於<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags.PrimaryInteropAssembly?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, at least one of these parameters must be specified.
trans-unit.target: 否則，至少其中一個參數必須指定。

trans-unit.source: If `publicKey` is `null`, the public key in `keyPair` will be set in the target assembly's manifest metadata and a signature will be generated based on the contents of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 如果`publicKey`是`null`中的公開金鑰`keyPair`會設定在目標組件資訊清單中繼資料，而且會產生簽章的組件內容為基礎。

trans-unit.source: If `keyPair` is `null`, `publicKey` will be set in the target assembly's manifest metadata and no signature will be generated.
trans-unit.target: 如果`keyPair`是`null`，`publicKey`會設定在目標組件資訊清單中繼資料，而且會產生沒有簽章。

trans-unit.source: Specifying both parameters is not generally useful, and can result in an invalid signature.
trans-unit.target: 指定這兩個參數通常很有用，並不會導致無效的簽章。

trans-unit.source: For more information on `ITypeLib`, please see its existing documentation in the MSDN library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`ITypeLib`，請參閱 MSDN library 中的現有文件。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="typeLib" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="typeLib" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="asmFileName" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asmFileName" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="notifySink" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="notifySink" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="asmFileName" /> is an empty string.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asmFileName" /> 為空字串。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="asmFileName" /> is longer than MAX_PATH.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asmFileName" /> 比 MAX_PATH 更長。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="flags" /> is not <see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags.PrimaryInteropAssembly" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="flags" /> 不是 <see cref="F:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags.PrimaryInteropAssembly" />。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="publicKey" /> and <paramref name="keyPair" /> are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="publicKey" /> 和 <paramref name="keyPair" /> 是 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The metadata produced has errors preventing any types from loading.
trans-unit.target: 所產生的中繼資料具有阻止任何型別載入的錯誤。

trans-unit.source: The version of the resulting assembly.
trans-unit.target: 產生組件的版本。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="null" />, the version of the type library is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果為 <see langword="null" />，則使用型別程式庫的版本。
